</span> </span> <span class="meta-tags" title="Tags"> <i class="icon-tags"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/carlo-lepore/" rel="tag">carlo lepore</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/carlos-alvarez/" rel="tag">Carlos Alvarez</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/carmela-remigio/" rel="tag">Carmela Remigio</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/christopher-hogwood/" rel="tag">Christopher Hogwood</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/don-giovanni/" rel="tag">Don Giovanni</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/eva-mei/" rel="tag">Eva Mei</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/federico-longhi/" rel="tag">Federico Longhi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/jose-antonio-garcia/" rel="tag">José Antonio Garcia</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/maurizo-balo/" rel="tag">Maurizo Balò</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/michele-placido/" rel="tag">Michele Placido</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/rocio-ignacio/" rel="tag">Rocio Ignacio</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/tomislav-muzek/" rel="tag">Tomislav Muzek</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/wolfgang-amadeus-mozart/" rel="tag">Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="carlo lepore, Carlos Alvarez, Carmela Remigio, Christopher Hogwood, Don Giovanni, Eva Mei, Federico Longhi, José Antonio Garcia, Maurizo Balò, Michele Placido, Opera lirica, Rocio Ignacio, Tomislav Muzek, Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b41b40d04cc32e3e4f904f051c19deec" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Michele-Curnis-120x150.jpg" width="80" height="100" alt="Michele Curnis" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-av